Search in Array:
Given an array of integers, find the index of a specific element.

Maximum Element:
Find the maximum element in an array and its index.

Minimum Element:
Find the minimum element in an array and its index.

Count Occurrences:
Count the number of occurrences of a specific element in an array.

First Occurrence:
Find the index of the first occurrence of a specific element in an array.

Last Occurrence:
Find the index of the last occurrence of a specific element in an array.

Element Frequency:
Find the frequency of each element in an array.

Sum of Elements:
Calculate the sum of all elements in an array.

Average of Elements:
Calculate the average of all elements in an array.

Element Existence:
Check if a specific element exists in an array.